      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking low-cost transportation without the premium price tag. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for someone who values utility and value over perfection, but it still offers solid everyday potential at an accessible price point. A sensible opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone needing budget-friendly wheels.",
