      "description": "Looking for an affordable car you can put to work right away or turn into a great little project? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. A good fit for someone who wants cheap wheels, a backup vehicle, or something to tinker with without spending a fortune. Priced fairly and ready for its next chapter.",
